CM_ SG_ 2462364673 POS_V2_3_CurrDirectionLanes "Information for the Number of lanes in driving direction of current position";
CM_ SG_ 2462364673 POS_V2_3_CurrSpeedLimit "Information for Current Link Speed Limit of current position expressed as kph or mph according to META_SpeedUnit";
