CM_ BO_ 2462366209 "[EC] On Event and On Change";
CM_ SG_ 2462366209 PROSHORT_V2_3_Offset "Information for Offset of position of the first profile spot from currnet position
-This Offset should be calculated using below Factors(according to Profile Type)
-Profile Type 1(Curvature): 1m
-Profile Type 4(Slope): 1m(PROSHORT_Accuracy=0x0), 3m(PROSHORT_Accuracy=0x2)
-Profile Type 16(Safety Driving Section): 1m(Section0,1,2,3,5)
-Refer to Specification(ES96523-31) for details";
CM_ SG_ 2462366209 PROSHORT_V2_3_PathIndex "Information for Index of the path where this profile is located";
CM_ SG_ 2462366209 PROSHORT_V2_3_Distance "Information for Distance from first profile spot to the second one
-This distance should be calculated using below Factors(according to Profile Type)
-Profile Type 1(Curvature): 2
-Profile Type 4(Slope): 2(PROSHORT_Accuracy=0x0), 20(PROSHORT_Accuracy=0x2)
-Profile Type 16(Safety Driving Section): 20(Section0,1), 2(Section2,3), 5(Section5)";
CM_ SG_ 2462366209 PROSHORT_V2_3_Value0 "Information for Profile Short value at Offset";
CM_ SG_ 2462366209 PROSHORT_V2_3_Value1 "Information for Profile Short value at Offset+Distance1";
CM_ SG_ 2462366209 PROSHORT_V2_3_ProfileType "Information for Profile Short Type: Slope(Linear) is used for Slope
-In case of Section Speed, transmitt Average Value of Speed Limit of Links in Section.
-Link without Speed Limit is excluded for Average Speed Calculation
-Unlimited Lane in Europe reflects 140kph for Average Speed Calculation";
CM_ SG_ 2462366209 PROSHORT_V2_3_CyclicCounter "Information for Cyclic counter of this message type and profile type: Reconstructor can use this value to detect missing messages.
-According to Profile Type, transmitt different Cyclic Counter Values
-In case of Slope, transmitt Cyclic Counter Values according to the Slope Transmitting Specification
 (Refer to 5.4 Slope Information Transmitting Scenario in Specification: It is about Information for Average Slope(Maximum 3) Transmitting by Event in forward unit distance(2km/20km) containing Current Location)
-In case of 'PROSHORT_CyclicCounter', transmitt particularly according to the 'PROSHORT_ProfileType'
 Ex) ProfileType(CyclicCounter): 0x1(0)  0x1(1)  0x10(0)  0x1(2)  0x10(1) ...";
CM_ SG_ 2462366209 PROSHORT_V2_3_Accuracy "Information for Accuracy of profile value is implementation specific.";
CM_ BO_ 2462365953 "[EC] On Event and On Change";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_Offset "Information for Offset of this Segment from current position";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_PathIndex "Information for Index of path of which this segment is part";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_CalculatedRoute "Information for Calculated Route: MPP/On Route/Off Route(Recalculating Route)
-MPP: Predicted Route(Not the Link from Searched Route). Used if users donˇŻt set Destination. Used with Current Link Information.
-On Route: Link from Searched Route. Used with Current Link Information.
-Off Route: Used when trying to enter the Rest Area. 'SEG_CalculatedRoute', 'SEG_FormOfWay' and 'SEG_FunctionalRoadClass' are used together. But if it is impossible to decide values of 'SEG_FormOfWay' and 'SEG_FunctionalRoadClass', transmitt Unknown Value. If additional Information happens in forward unit distance, retransmitt it by Event.";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_FuncRoadClass "Information for Functional Road Class indicates relative importance of the road in the routing network and lower values indicate higher priority";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_SpeedLimit "Information for Current Link Speed Limit expressed as km/h or mph according to META_SpeedUnit";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_FormOfWay "Information for Link Class Value of Segment";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_DirectionLanes "Information for the Number of lanes in driving direction";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_SpeedLimitUnder5 "Current Link Speed Limit of less than 5 kph or mph according to META_SpeedUnit";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_DividedRoad "Inform whether there is a Physical Separation on the road";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_CyclicCounter "Information for Cyclic counter of this message type: Reconstructor can use this value to detect missing messages";
CM_ SG_ 2462365953 SEG_V2_3_Retransmission "Information for Retransmission Flag: If true, this message was sent already at least once before.";
