BA_ "Description" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshInfo "1)When crash output is issued, this signal is transmitted as 0x2. 
2)When crash output is not issued and ACU meets MCB requirement of ESC.  this signal is transmitted as 0x1.

Just then If ACU receives feedback signal from ESC this signal is transmitted as 0x0.
If ACU do NOT receive feedback signal from ESC previous signal value is maintaned.

ˇŘThis signal is transmmited until power-off";
BA_ "GenSigSendType" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshInfo 2;
BA_ "GenSigStartValue" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshInfo 0;
BA_ "UserSigValidity" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshInfo 3;
BA_ "NetworkRequestHoldingTime" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshInfo 0;
BA_ "RoutingFactor" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshInfo 1;
BA_ "Version" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshInfo "19.02.06";
BA_ "Description" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshTyp "This signal indicates types of  crash. 
If a collision occurs continuously at same IGN cycle each crash type bit set to 1 according to the type of collision.

1)First byte Information 
xxxx xxxxB : No deployment Crash (Crash output signal not issued)
xxxx xxx1B : Front Crash (First stage only)
xxxx xx1xB : Front Crash (Full stage)
xxxx x1xxB : Side Crash (Driver side) 
xxxx 1xxxB : Side Crash (Passenger side)
xxx1 xxxxB : Rollover Crash (Restraints activation)
xx1x xxxxB : Rollover event information transmission (Restraints non-activation)
x1xx xxxxB : Side Crash Detection For Door Unlock (NON-SAB vehicle)
1xxx xxxxB : Rear Crash 
2)Second byte information 
xxxx xxx1B : Pre Crash (Pretentioner or Pretentioner + KAB)
other bits : RESERVED
ˇŘx means that Not set as 1
ˇŘFor example, If Driver side crash occurs and then Front crash-full stage occurs  continuously, Type of crash bit set to 0000 0000 0000 0110B";
BA_ "GenSigSendType" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshTyp 2;
BA_ "GenSigStartValue" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshTyp 0;
BA_ "UserSigValidity" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshTyp 3;
BA_ "NetworkRequestHoldingTime" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshTyp 0;
BA_ "RoutingFactor" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshTyp 1;
BA_ "Version" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshTyp "19.02.06";
