0x1: Temporary unavailable by Front View Camera (blockage, high temperature, etc) for Sensor Fusion FCA 
0x2: Temporary unavailable by Front Radar (blockage, high temperature, etc) for either Radar only FCA or Sensor Fusion FCA when logic is in Front Radar
0x3: System failure (Failure by Front View Camera failure, Front Radar failure or relative cooperative control units, etc)
0x4: Temporary unavailable by Front View Camera (blockage, high temperature, etc) for Front View Camera only FCA
0x5: Temporary unavailable of steering function by Front View Camera (blockage, high temperature, etc) for sensor fusion when logic is in ADAS_DRV
