BA_ "Description" SG_ 2239849729 PA_ModDis "This signal is used for PA/PDW display ON/OFF.
The value is sended to be based on the PA/PDW internal activation status, not the only switch status.
This means that the signal value should be OFF in case of PA/PDW internal activation status OFF, although PA/PDW switch is ON.

<Fuction>
0H : PA OFF, PDW OFF
1H : PA OFF, PDW ON
2H : PA ON, PDW OFF
3H : PA ON, PDW ON";
