BA_ "Version" SG_ 2239849730 PA_TestModSta "17.11.00";
BA_ "Description" SG_ 2239849730 PA_StrAnglReq "This value is used to set a steering wheel position target for the PA function. The signal is signed 16bits.

Conversion: (PH) = (HEX) x 0.1 (for 0< HEX < 32767) OR
(HEX - 65536) x 0.1 (for HEX > 32767)";
