BA_ "Description" SG_ 1030 APSM_SWVerMajor1 "Indicate the SCM software version as follows:
- The software version is displayed in three digits.
- The Major and Minor digits are separated by '.'
- Signal values are transmitted to ASCII codes.

ˇŘ Example
APSM_SWVerMajor1 : 0x41 (HEX) -> ASCII CODE : 'A' 
APSM_SWVerMinor1 : 0x30 (HEX) -> ASCII CODE : '0'
APSM_SWVerMinor2 : 0x33 (HEX) -> ASCII CODE : '3'
=> APSM S/W Ver is displayed 'A.03'";
BA_ "GenSigSendType" SG_ 1030 APSM_SWVerMajor1 4;
BA_ "GenSigStartValue" SG_ 1030 APSM_SWVerMajor1 0;
BA_ "UserSigValidity" SG_ 1030 APSM_SWVerMajor1 0;
