BA_ "Description" SG_ 963 IBU_SWVerMajor1 "Indicate the IBU software version as follows:
- The software version is displayed in three digits.
- The Major and Minor digits are separated by '.'
- Signal values are transmitted to ASCII codes.

ˇŘ Example
C_IBU_SWVerMajor1 : 0x41 (HEX) -> ASCII CODE : 'A' 
C_IBU_SWVerMinor1 : 0x30 (HEX) -> ASCII CODE : '0'
C_IBU_SWVerMinor2 : 0x33 (HEX) -> ASCII CODE : '3'
=> IBU S/W Ver is displayed 'A.03'";
