BA_ "Description" SG_ 2256644610 CLU_CUSTOMSta_NEW "This is a signal for New concept CUSTOM mode in AVN USM
This is a confirm signal for selecting CUSTOM mode in AVN USM
And Other units refer this signal when CUSTOM mode (CLU_DrvngModSwSta=0x6
). Other unit decided the Detailed CUSTOM Mode with this signal
EX>
 In AVN USM, MY DRIVE MODE is selected, sent CLU_CUSTOMSta_NEW= 0x1
In vehicle, current mode is MY DRIVE MODE, other unit refer this signal and decide detailed Mode.In this case, MY DRIVE MODE is a mode";
