BA_ "Description" SG_ 2290230530 CLU_SRSWrngLmpSta "This signal is generated by one of the following 5 self-diagnostic result of micro-controller of Cluster.
1) ˇ°Lamp ONˇ± status as a self-status diagnostic result of cluster
2) ˇ°Lamp OFFˇ± status as a self-status diagnostic result of cluster
3) ˇ°Lamp flashing with 1hz frequency / 50% duty ratioˇ± as a self-status result diagnostic result of cluster
4) ˇ°Lamp Circuit Failureˇ± as a self-diagnostic result of cluster circuit 
5) ˇ°No Valid ACU messageˇ± as ACU4 message check result by cluster

Note to be taken that CLU2 message does not include judgment on ˇ°SRS W/Lamp failure in terms of airbag systemˇ±. CLU2 message only contains ˇ°status and diagnostic result of Cluster itselfˇ±.";
