BA_ "Description" SG_ 2395189761 DATC_Opt3Typ "This signal indicates Option of HTR Control.

Bit0~1 (Button Type)  : 0 ? Not Display in AVN /
                              1 ? Single (Blower-Temp-Mode) /
                              2 ? Single (Temp-Mode-Blower) / 
                              3 ? Dual ˇ¤ 3zone ˇ¤ 4zone / 
Bit2 : 0 - Defogging USM Not Apply / 1 - Defogging USM Apply 
Bit3 : 0 - Automatic Ventilation USM Not Apply / 1 - Automatic Ventilation USM Apply
Bit4 : 0 ? Auto AirCleaningSystem USM Not Apply / 1 - Auto AirCleaningSystem USM Apply
Bit5 : 0 ? Washer fluid Control USM Not Apply / 1 - Washer fluid Control USM Apply
Bit6~7 : 0 - Haptic Intensity USM Not Apply 
              1 - Haptic Intensity USM Apply (3-Level)
              2 - Haptic Intensity USM Apply (5-Level)
              3 - Reserved
0xFF : Invalid";
