BA_ "Version" SG_ 2395189761 DATC_Opt2Typ "21.07.06";
BA_ "Description" SG_ 2395189761 DATC_Opt4Typ "This signal indicates Option of HTR Control.

Bit0 (Driver Only Button) :  0 ? NOT Apply / 1 ? Apply
Bit1 (HEAT Button) :  0 ? NOT Apply / 1 ? Apply
Bit2 (Multi-Air Mode) : 0 ? Not Apply / 1 - Apply
Bit3 : (Scheduled Ventilation) : 0 ? Not Apply / 1 ? Apply
