BA_ "Description" SG_ 2365803009 DATC_Typ2 "Bit0: (AVN Controllable) :  0 ? NOT Apply / 1 ? Apply
Bit1~2 (Multi Auto Blower) : 0 ? Single / 1 ? 2 Step Type / 2 ? 3 Step Type  / 3 - Reserved
Bit3~5 (Front Mode Type) : 0 ? 4 MODE / 1 ? 6MODE / 2 ? 7MODE  / 3 ~ 7 ? Reserved
Bit6 (Fine Dust Sensor) : 0 - Fine Dust Sensor Not Applied / 1 - Fine Dust Sensor Applied.
Bit7~8 (Multi Auto Text) : 0 - Multi Auto State Text Not Applied / 1 - Multi Auto State Text Display Only Applied / 2 - Multi Auto State Text Display & Control Applied / 3 ? Reserved
Bit9 (Mode Def Type) : 0 ? Symbol Type / 1 ? Arrow Type
Bit10~15 : Reserved";
