BA_ "Description" SG_ 2193667330 ENG_EtcLmphModSta "When ETC Mal-function occurred, EMS requests Cluster to indicate limphome mode driving and inform driver to go to AS center as soon as possible.
- In case of ETC malfunction, EMS finishes ETC control so that a vehicle goes to limphome mode driving (Forced idle). Since sudden vehicle speed decrease can cause uncomfortable feeling to driver, EMS needs to indicate limphome mode condition on Cluster to induce driver to go to AS center as soon as possible.";
BA_ "GenSigStartValue" SG_ 2193667330 ENG_EtcLmphModSta 0;
