BA_ "Description" SG_ 2193667331 ENG_TrgtIdleRpmVal "The stationary target speed depends principally of the engine coolant temperature.
There is a difference between the target speed for manual transmission MT and automatic transmission (AT) in ˇŻneutralˇŻ and AT in ˇŻdriveˇŻ. 
- Immediately after start the catalyst heating function may increase the target speed 
- The battery charge monitoring increase the target speed.
- For A/C use the target speed may be increased";
