BA_ "Description" SG_ 2214658049 ENG_BrkSwSta "This signal indicates that a brake switch is activated or not. When the brake switch is activated(pressed) its value is 01H otherwise its value is 00H.
If the EMS does not support this signal the value is 02H.

Physical range : 0 ... 100
Conversion : (PH) = (Unsigned)0.002 * (HEX)[%]";
