BA_ "Description" SG_ 2307022850 SCC_SccFlrDetSta "When it is set, the signal indicates that EMS cannot accept the engine torque request for SCC, TQI_ACC, because of a failure or failures in EMS which may be recovered within the same ignition cycle. EMS stores DTC for the failure.
In case that there is no failure or the failure is cleared, the signal gets reset.";
