BA_ "Version" SG_ 2307022850 SCC_SccFlrDetSta "17.12.00";
BA_ "Description" SG_ 2307022850 OBD_RbmSta "For the calculation of the denominators for Rate-Based Monitoring(RBM), CARB defined the standardized vehicle operations, which must be met to increment the denominator counter.
So, this variable is to give a status information(fulfilled or not) about all conditions for the standardized
vehicle operations.

Bit0 : Minimum trip length condition
Bit1 : Vehicle speed condition
Bit2 : Continuous idle condition
Bit3 : Ambient temperature condition
Bit4 : Maximum altitude condition
Bit5 : Reserved
Bit6 : Reserved";
BA_ "GenSigStartValue" SG_ 2307022850 OBD_RbmSta 0;
BA_ "UserSigValidity" SG_ 2307022850 OBD_RbmSta 3;
BA_ "NetworkRequestHoldingTime" SG_ 2307022850 OBD_RbmSta 0;
