BA_ "Description" SG_ 415 FPM_FPEnrollState "Fingerprint Enrollment processing state. 
- Touch : Place a finger on the Start/Stop button sensor
- Lift : Lift a finger off
- AdjustPosition : For the best results, move the finger upward or downward slightly between attempts. 
- Try Touch Again : Place the fingerprint again
- Processing : Enrollment process is working
- Completed : Enrollment process success
- Failed : Enrollment process fail";
