BA_ "Description" SG_ 1049 ICU_BS1IBAT_Conversion "This is Battery current as measured by battery sensor.
The resolution is 10mA

- 0x3FFFF : 262,143 (Error) , 0x00000 ~ 0x3A980 : 0 ~ 240,000
- Physical value min. : (0 * 10mA) + (-1,200,000) = -1,200 A
- Physical value max. : (240,000 * 10mA) + (-1,200,000) = 1,200 A";
