BA_ "Description" SG_ 2449771009 ODS_DiagSta "CR_WCS_Errstat signal describes PODS-G & BOSE system error that is diagnosed by itself. Each Type set Diagnostic Status explains 3 kinds of fault.
[PODS-G]
Bit 1 : If ODS Have some errors, ODS set the bit, sends the ALR Defect signal to ACU and notifies the fault.
Bit 2 : If ODS Have some errors, ODS set the bit, sends the ECU Defect signal to ACU and notifies the fault.
Bit 5 : If ODS Have some errors, ODS set the bit, sends the EOL Error signal to ACU and notifies the fault.

[BOSE]
Bit 1 : If ODS Have some errors, ODS set the bit, sends the Mat Defect signal to ACU and notifies the fault.
Bit 2 : If ODS Have some errors, ODS set the bit, sends the ECU Defect signal to ACU and notifies the fault.
Bit 6 : If ODS Have some errors, ODS set the bit, sends the Algo Cut-off Error signal to ACU and notifies the fault.";
BA_ "GenSigStartValue" SG_ 2449771009 ODS_DiagSta 0;
BA_ "UserSigValidity" SG_ 2449771009 ODS_DiagSta 3;
BA_ "NetworkRequestHoldingTime" SG_ 2449771009 ODS_DiagSta 0;
BA_ "RoutingFactor" SG_ 2449771009 ODS_DiagSta 1;
BA_ "Version" SG_ 2449771009 ODS_DiagSta "17.12.02";
