BA_ "Version" SG_ 2223056129 SAS_SpdVal "18.12.08";
BA_ "Description" SG_ 2223056129 SAS_IntSta "Information regarding the steering angle sensorˇŻs internal state. If SAS_AnglVal value is O.K., SAS_OK flag is set and otherwise SAS_OK flag is cleared. If steering angle sensor has been calibrated, SAS_CAL flag is set and otherwise cleared.
SF1 - SF5 : for internal use only

SAS_OK(=1), SAS_CAL(=1) : SAS_AnglVal(=value), SAS_SpdVal(=value)
SAS_OK(=1), SAS_CAL(=0) : SAS_AnglVal(=7FFFh), SAS_SpdVal(=value)
SAS_OK(=0), SAS_CAL(=1) : SAS_AnglVal(=7FFFh), SAS_SpdVal(=FFh)
SAS_OK(=0), SAS_CAL(=0) : SAS_AnglVal(=7FFFh), SAS_SpdVal(=FFh)

ˇŘ If SAS is trimmed, SAS_Trim flag = 1.
If SAS is not trimmed (in this case SAS_OK=0 and SAS_CAL=0), SAS_Trim flag=0.";
BA_ "GenSigStartValue" SG_ 2223056129 SAS_IntSta 14;
