BA_ "Description" SG_ 2164277249 TCU_GearStepTyp "This signal indicates number of gear steps of step type automatic transmission(A/T) or Dual Clutch Transmission(DCT). A vehicle can have A/T or DCT variant according to its option, for example 4-speed A/T or 5-speed A/T can be equipped in the same kind of vehicles and other control systems (e.g. ESC, TCS, ˇ¦) can need this information to apply appropriate control logic.

The CVT (Continuously Variable Transmission) should set this signal to 00H.";
BA_ "GenSigStartValue" SG_ 2164277249 TCU_GearStepTyp 0;
