BA_ "Description" SG_ 2164277250 TCU_FuelCutInhbtReq "During coast down shifting, EMS may cut off fuel injection and as a result, a driver can feel bad shift feeling. In this case, to enhance shift quality, TCU needs inhibition of fuel cut off control.
This signal indicates inhibition of engine fuel cut off control.";
