BA_ "Version" SG_ 2164277250 TCU_FuelCutInhbtReq "17.11.00";
BA_ "Description" SG_ 2164277250 TCU_IdleUpReq "When ATF(Automatic Transmission Fluid) rises in high temperauture, the TCU requests engine idle RPM up via the signal IDLE_UP_TCU to the EMS for reduction of gearshift time form Neutral to Reverse.

